explode=[]
for i in range(len(data['Type 1'].unique())):
    explode.append(0.05)
data['Type 1'].value_counts().plot(kind='pie', explode=explode, autopct='%1.1f%%')
fig=plt.gcf()
fig.set_size_inches(15, 15)
plt.show()

top_types=data['Type 1'].value_counts().head(10).reset_index()
